<item>
            <title>[LU-19891] sanity test_160a-160u: FAIL: changelog_mask=+hsm failed: 2</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19891</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;CLOSED &#8212; Duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19750&quot; title=&quot;interop: master+b2_15 client can&amp;#39;t access changelog due to missing mdt_body in open request&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19750&quot;&gt;LU-19750&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The initial report that this was a master-on-master regression was in error. All failing sessions on lustre-master are interop (master el10 client + b2_16 server). The lustre-reviews failures were from broken &quot;custom&quot; test sessions with widespread environmental issues (116 failures total).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See comments for full investigation. Root cause is the mdt_changelog_allow() / mdt_body interop issue tracked in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19750&quot; title=&quot;interop: master+b2_15 client can&amp;#39;t access changelog due to missing mdt_body in open request&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19750&quot;&gt;LU-19750&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Original description:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity tests 160a through 160u fail on master with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;changelog_mask=+hsm failed: 2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The error indicates that &lt;tt&gt;lctl set_param mdd.*.changelog_mask=+hsm&lt;/tt&gt; returns ENOENT (rc=2).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example session: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b89c7bfa-710b-4425-87d8-caddf94cbe50&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b89c7bfa-710b-4425-87d8-caddf94cbe50&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Example test set: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/18c1a460-f896-462c-969f-c4443c14eab8&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/18c1a460-f896-462c-969f-c4443c14eab8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
